Class RawTextProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.AnnotatedText
      • com.joliciel.talismane.rawText.RawTextProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CurrentFileObserver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RawText, RollingTextBlock

    public abstract class RawTextProcessor
extends AnnotatedText
implements CurrentFileObserver
    A class capable of processing a set of RawTextFilters so that a list of sentences can be extracted.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
